Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: This property is UA. We had to separate from MLS # 73287167 for financing. Attention Investors! Feast your eyes on this rare offering—a three-unit building with an extra lot for parking strategically located for maximum tenant convenience. The property, comprising two three-family houses and a third parcel for parking (3 tax bills), has been lovingly maintained by long-term owners. Although below market (all TAWs), the current rents suggest a potential monthly income of $22K ($264K/Year) with just a hint of cosmetic work in two apartments. All units have two beds and two baths. The location is just two blocks from the West Broadway shops and minutes from the Seaport.
